The city of Ilorin, as well as Kwara State in general, was literally on fire on Sunday when lovers of entertainment in the state and beyond were thrilled to an evening of fun, music, and dance. The event, which roused the anticipation of many in Ilorin and beyond was graced by some of the biggest acts in the entertainment industry, with popular On-Air Personality and entertainer VJ Adams and music acts such as Lyta and Picazo among those who performed. With attractions such as non-stop music, food stalls, games, party, and performances, The Connect Party was aimed at bringing vibes to the city of Ilorin, connect the youths, influencers, and celebrities to foster togetherness and enterprise. Kwara screens 4,028 women for breast, cervical cancer Foundation to support traders with N250m loan 9m children benefit from school feeding programme ―… Kwara governor removes heads of state-owned media ALSO READ: More coronavirus deaths in Iran, Japan, South Korea raise pandemic fears The event added to the growing social life of the state capital, especially as it continued to harness the entertainment potentials in the state. With Ilorin being a city teeming with youthful population amid the host of tertiary institutions in the city, youths and fun lovers alike had unforgettable entertainment experience. The maiden edition of the event held at Kwara Hotel Field, Ilorin gave the people more than they bargained for. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXIER SEX WITH NAFDAC APPROVED JAMES BOND. 